"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-best-getty-images-2024-paris-olympics-week-3\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Between the Opening and Closing Ceremonies of the\\u00c22024 Paris Olympics,\\u00c2Getty Images\\u00c2will have a team of more than 80 photographers shooting\\u00c2as many as 5 million images.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Opening and Closing Ceremonies\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2Getty Images\\u00c2will\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 88}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 80 photographers\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"shooting\\u00c2as many as 5 million images\", \"from\": 131, \"to\": 167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those breathtaking photos are then run through a team of more than 40 editors, live-editing remotely from offices in London.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999997594545965, \"rank\": 2.4054055398368896e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those breathtaking photos\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 40 editors\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"offices\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a massive undertaking, a complex amalgamation of human ingenuity and artistic vision with radical technology \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 top-of-the-line lenses, remote cameras, robotic and underwater cameras and more.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive undertaking\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"a complex amalgamation\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"human ingenuity\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic vision\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"the-line\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"remote cameras\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"robotic and underwater cameras\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The results are breathtaking and help bring all the emotion of excitement of the games to people around around the world.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The results\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"all the emotion\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FanSided is lucky enough to be partnering with Getty throughout these games and each week several photographers will be sharing some of their favorite photos with us and explaining the stories behind them.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FanSided\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\"}, {\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999844258128, \"rank\": 1.4572412293666007e-08, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"several photographers\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite photos\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"the stories\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are Elsa, Jared C. Tilton and Clive Rose sharing what they captured in the final week.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\", \"score\": 0.9999991767043618, \"rank\": 8.232945166172791e-07, \"text\": \"Elsa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elsa_the_lioness\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Rose_(diplomat)\", \"score\": 0.6435637216196579, \"rank\": 0.553846153846337, \"text\": \"Clive Rose\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Rose_(diplomat)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Rose_(diplomat)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jared C. Tilton\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the final week\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay tuned for a full round-up of all the best images from the games after the closing ceremonies.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full round-up\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"all the best images\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is my fourth Summer Olympic Games as a staff photographer for Getty Images.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999844258128, \"rank\": 1.4572412293666007e-08, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fourth Summer Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"a staff photographer\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is a fabulous city with incredible venues.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4912013508464035e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fabulous city\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible venues\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a photographer, it has been amazing and at the same time a grueling grind.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photographer\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is easy to navigate by train and the grind is similar to my home base of New York \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 but much more intense.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4912013508464035e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999543965724, \"rank\": 4.5603510619015885e-08, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"train\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the grind\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1272}, {\"ngram\": \"my home base\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am covering different events each day so my gear pack varies with my assignments.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different events\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"my gear pack\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"my assignments\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For most of the first week, I was covering assignments solo.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first week\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"assignments solo\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This second week I am working with a team of our photographers covering medal events.\\u00c2 So far my favorite venue has been the beach volleyball \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 situated next to the iconic Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"our photographers\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"medal events\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"my favorite venue\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach volleyball\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone was chasing a sunset picture from the top of the stadium.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"a sunset picture\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did as well but also wanted to get a version from down below to be a bit different than the rest.\\u00c2 At some events, I would join our photographers who were assigned to cover a specific sport throughout the games.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a version\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"some events\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"our photographers\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific sport\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would try and fill in where they were not to get a different angle.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different angle\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the case for the apparatus finals of Artistic Gymnastics.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999999979240783, \"rank\": 2.0741242140760977e-09, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"the apparatus finals\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the medal ceremony for the floor exercise, we had photographers at floor level and I went upstairs in the stands to find a different view.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal ceremony\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor exercise\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"photographers\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"floor level\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"a different view\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past few days, Simone Biles and Jordan Chiles had been singing the praises of Rebeca Andrade and I had a feeling they would do something special.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2280, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past few days\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"the praises\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"a feeling\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What I love about his image is it shows what the Olympics and especially gymnastics are all about \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 athletes supporting one another.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his image\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"especially gymnastics\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 athletes\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To me this image embodies the Olympic spirit perfectly.\\u00c2 For athletics, I was stationed just after the start of the 200m and the last turn of the Women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400m hurdles.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this image\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"the last turn\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2667}, {\"ngram\": \"the Women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 400m hurdles\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oftentimes, the medalists will do a victory lap so being in that spot was great for capturing those moments as Sydney McLaughlin-Leverone did her victory lap after she won gold and set a World Record.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999406769514193, \"rank\": 5.932442884287272e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oftentimes\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"the medalists\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory lap\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"that spot\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"those moments\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"her victory lap\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"a World Record\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also got the chance to shoot badminton for a day.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not as easy as it looks!\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They return their shots so fast.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their shots\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I used a 50mm 1.2 lens and shot it at 1.2.\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 50mm 1.2 lens\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love to use the bokeh of fast primes to make challenging backgrounds beautiful.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bokeh\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"fast primes\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"challenging backgrounds\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t sure about this lens at first, but it is fast becoming a favorite in my camera bag.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this lens\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"my camera bag\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love reaction images.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reaction images\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we can connect more as humans with them.\\u00c2 I love reaction images the best in sports photography.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"sports photography\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is easier to make that human connection to what they are feeling.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that human connection\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I try to get both the joy of victory and the agony of defeat in a single image as that tells the whole story.\\u00c2 As a motorsport photographer, I was ecstatic to find out that I would be a part of our cycling coverage for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.236663586811303e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both the joy\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3473}, {\"ngram\": \"the agony\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"a single image\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole story\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3545}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"a motorsport photographer\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3627}, {\"ngram\": \"our cycling coverage\", \"from\": 3631, \"to\": 3651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although I had never covered a cycling event as an editorial photographer, I felt it would be right up my avenue after covering NASCAR and Formula 1 for many, many years.\\u00c2 There are some similarities to the overall coverage of racing, whether it be on a bike or in a sports car.\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3797, \"end\": 3803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"score\": 0.9999961382633942, \"rank\": 3.807983439475737e-06, \"text\": \"NASCAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NASCAR\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cycling event\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3713}, {\"ngram\": \"an editorial photographer\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"my avenue\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3781}, {\"ngram\": \"Formula\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3815}, {\"ngram\": \"many, many years\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3838}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3840}, {\"ngram\": \"some similarities\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3868}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall coverage\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3892}, {\"ngram\": \"racing\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3902}, {\"ngram\": \"a bike\", \"from\": 3921, \"to\": 3927}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports car\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarities such as understanding the racing line or identifying key moments in a race have allowed me to have an advantage in an unfamiliar sport.\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 4097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Similarities\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"the racing line\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3999}, {\"ngram\": \"key moments\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4026}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4036}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 4061, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"an unfamiliar sport\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With those similarities have also been some challenges to covering a sport at its highest level for the first time.\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those similarities\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4121}, {\"ngram\": \"some challenges\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4152}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 4165, \"to\": 4172}, {\"ngram\": \"its highest level\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daily preparation and the assistance of a great teammate have played a large role in understanding certain events in track and road cycling.\\u00c2 One of my favorite images from this week was a photo of the Peloton racing past The Louvre Museum during the Men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Road Race.\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4417, \"end\": 4424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2436689203932473e-11, \"text\": \"Peloton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peloton\"}, {\"begin\": 4441, \"end\": 4454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Louvre Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daily preparation\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"the assistance\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4250}, {\"ngram\": \"a great teammate\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4270}, {\"ngram\": \"a large role\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4295}, {\"ngram\": \"certain events\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"track and road cycling\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4353}, {\"ngram\": \"my favorite images\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4381}, {\"ngram\": \"this week\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4396}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"the Men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Road Race\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After photographing the start of the race at the base of the Eiffel Tower, I had to quickly take a metro and walk to the museum to ensure the prime center spot for this photo.\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4514}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4518, \"to\": 4526}, {\"ngram\": \"the base\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4538}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4558}, {\"ngram\": \"a metro\", \"from\": 4582, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"the museum\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"the prime center spot\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"this photo\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The center spot was key to the alignment of this very symmetrical composition.\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The center spot\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4676}, {\"ngram\": \"the alignment\", \"from\": 4688, \"to\": 4701}, {\"ngram\": \"this very symmetrical composition\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I arrived and waited four hours for a photo that happened in 20 seconds, then they were gone.\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four hours\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4783}, {\"ngram\": \"20 seconds\", \"from\": 4801, \"to\": 4811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest difference has been that there are not hundreds, or even dozens of laps to obtain your vision for most events.\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest difference\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 4893}, {\"ngram\": \"even dozens\", \"from\": 4898, \"to\": 4909}, {\"ngram\": \"laps\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4917}, {\"ngram\": \"your vision\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"most events\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 4955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You may only have one shot at creating that image, so the pressure is really on.\\u00c2 But, at the end of the day, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s still racing and I continue to try and show the speed and color of the sport the best I can.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one shot\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"that image\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5006}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 5011, \"to\": 5023}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5038}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5047, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5058, \"to\": 5065}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5073}, {\"ngram\": \"the speed\", \"from\": 5118, \"to\": 5127}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is what I personally like about the next two photos.\", \"from\": 5168, \"to\": 5225, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next two photos\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In one, the colors of the Olympic rings in the visor bring you into the photo and set a sense of place for the event.\", \"from\": 5226, \"to\": 5343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the colors\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5244}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 5248, \"to\": 5265}, {\"ngram\": \"the visor\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5278}, {\"ngram\": \"the photo\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5303}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5319}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5328}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the other, it not only brings the color and light in the venue to life but, it also shows the pure speed at which the athletes are competing.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d One of the best things about covering Artistic Swimming at the Olympics is that teams will perform new routines giving you something fresh to work with.\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the color\", \"from\": 5377, \"to\": 5386}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5396}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5409}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5413, \"to\": 5417}, {\"ngram\": \"the pure speed\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5451}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"the best things\", \"from\": 5499, \"to\": 5514}, {\"ngram\": \"Artistic Swimming\", \"from\": 5530, \"to\": 5547}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5563}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5577}, {\"ngram\": \"new routines\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5615, \"to\": 5624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You never really know what will happen when teams walk out to start their routines.\\u00c2 In this case, Team France, the home nation and first performance of the night, performed in a new costume that included faces on the back of their heads, which caught me by surprise initially as it looked very strange at first glance!\", \"from\": 5646, \"to\": 5966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5746, \"end\": 5757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999996216502, \"rank\": 3.742589890008299e-10, \"text\": \"Team France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 5690, \"to\": 5695}, {\"ngram\": \"their routines\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5729, \"to\": 5730}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 5734, \"to\": 5743}, {\"ngram\": \"the home nation\", \"from\": 5758, \"to\": 5773}, {\"ngram\": \"first performance\", \"from\": 5778, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 5799, \"to\": 5808}, {\"ngram\": \"a new costume\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"faces\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5856}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 5860, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"their heads\", \"from\": 5872, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"surprise\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5912}, {\"ngram\": \"first glance\", \"from\": 5952, \"to\": 5964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I decided to cover the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098land-based\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 part of the performance as nowadays this part of the performance can be quite interesting.\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 6097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098land-based\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 part\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 6011}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 6015, \"to\": 6030}, {\"ngram\": \"this part\", \"from\": 6043, \"to\": 6052}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 6056, \"to\": 6071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely added a unique aspect to the performance and makes you look deeper into the image.\", \"from\": 6098, \"to\": 6194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a unique aspect\", \"from\": 6118, \"to\": 6133}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 6137, \"to\": 6152}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s generally underappreciated the level of strength and fitness that is involved with Artistic Swimming.\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6294, \"end\": 6311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Synchronized_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Artistic Swimming\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Synchronized_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Synchronized_swimming\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6210}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 6238, \"to\": 6247}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 6251, \"to\": 6259}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 6264, \"to\": 6271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The work that happens under the water to produce spectacular aerial acrobatics during the routine is incredible, particularly if you keep in mind the entire time everyone\\u00e2\\u0080\